  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of APD811 in Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel-group, Placebo-controlled Phase 2 Trial of APD811, an Oral IP Receptor Agonist, in Patients With Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
