  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will be conducted as a placebo-controlled, randomized, 22 week double-blind study
      which will include a dose titration period. An additional transition period will occur for
      those patients who elect to enroll into the open-label extension study, APD811-007.
      Approximately 60 patients with PAH will be enrolled.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
